==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Idleness
<hw>I"dle*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>⟦imac⟧delnes</ets>.]</ety> <def>The condition or quality of being
idle (in the various senses of that word); uselessness; fruitlessness;
triviality; inactivity; laziness.</def></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Inaction; indolence; sluggishness;
sloth.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Idle-pated</ent>⟦br⟧
